Package: reel
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libmakemkv , makemkv-bin, reel-common
Description: DVD and Blu-ray ripping tool.
 Reel is a DVD and Blu-ray ripping tool that provides a user-friendly interface for
 managing the ripping process. It uses makemkvcon to perform the actual ripping tasks,
 and provides features such as progress tracking and error handling.

Package: reel-common
Architecture: all
Depends: reel
Description: Common files for reel.
 This package contains common files for the reel application, such as application icons
 and desktop files and documentation. These files are shared between the reel, reel-gtk,
 and reel-qt packages.

Package: reel-gtk
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 makemkv-bin, python3, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1,
 reel
Description: GTK Frontend for makemkvcon written in Python.
 Reel uses makemkvcon to rip DVDs and Blu-rays, and provides a user-friendly
 interface to manage the ripping process.

Package: reel-qt
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 makemkv-bin, python3, python3-pyqt5, reel
Description: Qt Frontend for makemkvcon written in Python.
 Reel uses makemkvcon to rip DVDs and Blu-rays, and provides a user-friendly
 interface to manage the ripping process.
